{"tid":2163560,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打八號波同黑雨既時候佢地去哂邊？","createTime":"2020-08-18T17:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T22:08:20.000Z","uid":60393,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8c4ecf53907364c6cae58c394631c18fa13679","tid":2163560,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"平日出街不難發現鳥兒滿天飛<br />\n鳥倦知還 飛到累硬係歸巢歇息<br />\n樹上既鳥巢就是牠們唯一的家<br />\n當天氣太惡劣<br />\n係打風落大雨既時候<br />\n樹蔭當然不能百分百阻擋暴雨既吞噬<br />\n平日從鳥巢傳來的吱吱聲彷彿被狂風奪去<br />\n其實鳥兒是否仍然安然無恙？<br />\n還是老早已躲至另一處？<br />\n請幫解答一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8a75462f08c1c839e46cb6d8c59a739826bf53","tid":2163560,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:46:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"733e0af4e96aa8c4f76cecd67ec619e84d0c7a96","tid":2163560,"uid":188129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:47:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e040e7d5ce0a23c1f72b875f23eb3cf538753a81","tid":2163560,"uid":336070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"已經9號波喎巴打～"},{"pid":"35a749b4903c15c3b3acf36d14ea2d6d2a5c1cb0","tid":2163560,"uid":133763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"你望下冷氣機頂<br />\n<br />\n一家大細喺晒度"},{"pid":"935584222ff0601ec6d006ad8ee82bb2b717a79e","tid":2163560,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e040e7d5ce0a23c1f72b875f23eb3cf538753a81","tid":2163560,"uid":336070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"已經9號波喎巴打～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"一樣姐"},{"pid":"9bf58996f205176cd69332a5ce07f4c163b3e5c6","tid":2163560,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1fdd21c27f1cdbcb61485ed0c0a77884280180","tid":